Madeline Zima https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madeline_Zima 0 Madeline Zima (born September 16, 1985) is an American actress. She is known for portraying Grace Sheffield on the CBS sitcom The Nanny (1993–1999), Mia Lewis on the Showtime comedy drama series Californication (2007–2011), and Gretchen Berg on the NBC series Heroes (2009–2010).
